27eb98b9015d0a96d","tid":1604730,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:36:16.000Z","msg":"經過咗三個月既香城足球隊我地都唔係大勝而回<br />\n反而敵方不斷改變踢波策略，導致手足輸左200比0。<br />\n所以我有以下嘅提議，唔知道可唔可行<br />\n歡迎所有參與玩香城足球隊朋友齊齊討論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陣營上有些少改變<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔知道有無效，大家一齊討論，為香城足球隊爭光，其他足球隊都支持緊大家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">驅逐共黨，還我香港</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"aaa93e1ab3479841c2e331aa7e58a801c8931d48","tid":1604730,"uid":2036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:40:06.000Z","msg":"推. 人多好做野"},{"pid":"40e6ae6f6948bdd678d07acec3378b970ee21b73","tid":1604730,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:42:37.000Z","msg":"發現有鬼第一時間唔係打... 而係...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1604858/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1604858/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"3d639bf849c7fe0c9aa4830288c9f88583909a5f","tid":1604730,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:23:13.000Z","msg":".."}]}